{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2d3b38f358","title":"中共中央关于同意修改减租暂行条例相关内容给西南局的批复","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"30258cc3bb","index":0,"year":1950,"month":3,"day":6,"articleId":"2d3b38f358"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"36ce55c5ab","type":"title","text":"中共中央关于同意修改减租暂行条例相关内容给西南局的批复","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2d3b38f358"},{"id":"8e0ef1ecbc","type":"paragraph","text":"西南局：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2d3b38f358"},{"id":"637d3a8e5c","type":"paragraph","text":"三月三日电悉。同意你们意见，减租暂行条例中减租百分之二十五至三十，删去“至三十”三字。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2d3b38f358"},{"id":"edeb973e7d","type":"paragraph","text":" 中央三月六日五时","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2d3b38f358"},{"id":"6ca9f9ae03","type":"paragraph","text":"附：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2d3b38f358"},{"id":"3662634d32","type":"subtitle","text":"西南局关于修改减租暂行条例中有关条文的请示","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2d3b38f358"},{"id":"d9ba05215e","type":"subtitle","text":"（一九五O年三月三日）","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2d3b38f358"},{"id":"ad80fc8da7","type":"paragraph","text":"中央：","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2d3b38f358"},{"id":"d6a197ce19","type":"paragraph","text":"《西南区减租暂行条例》，当遵照中央批示修改公布，惟第二条中规定一律照原租额减低百分之二十五至三十，我们再次考虑将“至三十”三字取消，即只提减百分之二十五。因为最近政务院文件提的是二五减租，同时鉴于干部思想条例[件]规定机动范围愈少愈好。是否有当，请速核示，以便公布。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2d3b38f358"},{"id":"083afdaf25","type":"paragraph","text":" 西南局寅江","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2d3b38f358"}],"page":{"id":"ec9e2c0f4d","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2d3b38f358","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}